.TH INSTALL-NONLAOS 1 "July 2026" "nonlaOS" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
install-nonlaos \- start the nonlaOS graphical installer
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B install-nonlaos
.RI [ arguments ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B install-nonlaos
starts Calamares with administrator privileges using
.BR pkexec (1).
It is intended for the nonlaOS live session desktop and application menu.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR calamares (8),
.BR pkexec (1)
